{"data":[{"date":"15:47 10/08","title":"Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Courtois \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ee3 c\u0169 \u0111\u1ebfn l\u1ec5 ra m\u1eaft Real Madrid","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/10/thu-mon-courtois-dua-vo-cu-den-le-ra-mat-real-madrid.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 g\u00e2y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd khi \u0111\u01b0a c\u1ea3 b\u00e0 x\u00e3 ly h\u00f4n t\u1edbi ng\u00e0y vui t\u1ea1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 T\u00e2y Ban Nha.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">Sau khi v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua cu\u1ed9c ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf t\u1ea1i b\u1ec7nh vi\u1ec7n Sanitas La Moraleja v\u00e0 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 6 n\u0103m, Courtois ra m\u1eaft t\u1ea1i Bernabeu v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a b\u1ed1 m\u1eb9, anh em, v\u1ee3 Marta Dominguez, hai con Alexandra v\u00e0 Nicholas.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Courtois \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ee3 c\u0169 \u0111\u1ebfn l\u1ec5 ra m\u1eaft Real Madrid h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Courtois \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ee3 c\u0169 \u0111\u1ebfn l\u1ec5 ra m\u1eaft Real Madrid h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/10/cc-2403-1533869484.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Gia \u0111\u00ecnh Courtois trong l\u1ec5 ra m\u1eaft \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. \u1ea2nh: NS.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCourtois cho bi\u1ebft anh \"ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 t\u1eeb khi c\u00f2n nh\u1ecf\". \"C\u1ea3m \u01a1n t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa. Nh\u1edd c\u00f3 Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch, c\u00e1c c\u1ed1 v\u1ea5n, gia \u0111\u00ecnh, b\u1ea1n b\u00e8 v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 m\u1eb9 c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c con t\u00f4i d\u00f9 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n b\u00ean nhau. Hala Madrid\".<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau khi ra m\u1eaft, Courtois ra s\u00e2n Bernabeu \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u00e0o kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3. Sau \u0111\u00f3, anh tham gia cu\u1ed9c h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o. Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n 26 tu\u1ed5i c\u0169ng c\u00f3 4 n\u0103m ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London, n\u01a1i anh gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c hai ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh, m\u1ed9t FA Cup v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t Cup Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nCourtois g\u1eb7p Marta Dominguez, qu\u1ed1c t\u1ecbch T\u00e2y Ban Nha, trong th\u1eddi gian anh kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Atletico Madrid \u1edf m\u1ed9t trung t\u00e2m mua s\u1eafm \u1edf ph\u00eda B\u1eafc th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4, n\u01a1i c\u00f4 l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t nh\u00e2n vi\u00ean b\u00e1n h\u00e0ng. Hai ng\u01b0\u1eddi gi\u1eef quan h\u1ec7 t\u00ecnh c\u1ea3m v\u00e0 c\u00f4ng khai v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 5/2014 trong ng\u00e0y vui Atletico Madrid \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Barca \u1edf s\u00e2n Nou Camp.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u00e0y, Courtois \u0111\u1ebfn Chelsea c\u00f9ng v\u1ee3 v\u00e0 hai ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 con \u0111\u1ea7u l\u00f2ng n\u0103m 2015. Th\u00e1ng 5/2017, \u0111\u1ee9a con th\u1ee9 hai ch\u00e0o \u0111\u1eddi nh\u01b0ng m\u1ed9t th\u00e1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, c\u1eb7p \u0111\u00f4i ly d\u1ecb.</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5335","checkdouble":"194182"},{"date":"15:54 10/08","title":"Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u01a1i t\u1eebng hai l\u1ea7n v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch thi\u2026 chim","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/10/thu-mon-dat-gia-nhat-the-gioi-tung-hai-lan-vo-dich-thi-chim.jpg","new_desc":"${8_news_content2}","new_url":"","id":"5334","checkdouble":"194184"},{"date":"15:57 10/08","title":"Sao tr\u1ebb Mbappe l\u1eafm m\u1ed1i t\u1ed1i n\u1eb1m kh\u00f4ng","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/10/sao-tre-mbappe-lam-moi-toi-nam-khong.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Th\u0103ng hoa tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ecf, Kylian Mbappe tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ec1 t\u00e0i khai th\u00e1c tr\u1ecdng \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi. Chuy\u1ec7n t\u00ecnh c\u1ea3m c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o 19 tu\u1ed5i ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00f4i ra m\u1ed5 x\u1ebb kh\u00f4ng thua chuy\u1ec7n \u0111\u00e1 banh. C\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u, Mbappe ch\u1eb3ng h\u1ec1 \u0111\u00e0o hoa nh\u01b0 b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi th\u00eau d\u1ec7t.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">Camille Gottlieb, con g\u00e1i c\u1ee7a c\u00f4ng ch\u00faa Monaco m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng \u0111\u00ednh ch\u00ednh tin \u0111\u1ed3n c\u1eb7p k\u00e8 v\u1edbi Mbappe. \u201cT\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 qu\u00e1 m\u1ec7t m\u1ecfi v\u1edbi tin \u0111\u1ed3n li\u00ean quan t\u1edbi Mbappe. Ch\u1eb3ng l\u1ebd t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ch\u1ee5p \u1ea3nh chung v\u1edbi anh ch\u00e0ng n\u00e0o m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t m\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi anh ta? \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng t\u00f4i tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec7n n\u00e0y. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec v\u1edbi Mbappe\u201d, Camille ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u tr\u00ean t\u1edd Nice-Matin.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/10/mbappe.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCamille l\u00e0 con g\u00e1i \u00fat c\u1ee7a St\u00e9phanie, c\u00f4ng ch\u00faa Monaco. Camille b\u1eb1ng tu\u1ed5i Mbappe (sinh n\u0103m 1998) v\u00e0 th\u1eeba h\u01b0\u1edfng nhan s\u1eafc qu\u00fd ph\u00e1i c\u1ee7a b\u00e0 ngo\u1ea1i l\u00e0 c\u00f4ng n\u01b0\u01a1ng ki\u00eam ng\u00f4i sao m\u00e0n b\u1ea1c Grace Kelly. H\u1ed3i th\u00e1ng 5/2017, Camille \u0111\u0103ng tr\u00ean Instagram t\u1ea5m \u1ea3nh ch\u1ee5p chung v\u1edbi ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o khi \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f2n kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Monaco l\u00e0m b\u00f9ng l\u00ean tin \u0111\u1ed3n v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c hai ng\u01b0\u1eddi qua l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi nhau. D\u00f9 Camille \u0111\u00e3 v\u00e0i l\u1ea7n ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn nh\u01b0ng tin \u0111\u1ed3n v\u1eabn lan r\u1ed9ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCamille kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng duy nh\u1ea5t b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed3n th\u1ed5i c\u00f3 quan h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi Mbappe. Hoa h\u1eadu Ph\u00e1p 2017, Alicia Aylies, c\u0169ng b\u1ecb cho l\u00e0 c\u00f3 m\u1ed1i li\u00ean h\u1ec7 t\u00ecnh c\u1ea3m v\u1edbi ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a PSG. T\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 v\u1eeba qua, Alicia \u0111\u00e3 bay sang Nga d\u1ef1 kh\u00e1n tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Ph\u00e1p v\u00e0 Argentina. B\u00e1o gi\u1edbi \u0111\u00e3 vin v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 cho r\u1eb1ng m\u1ef9 nh\u00e2n g\u1ed1c Martinique h\u1ebft l\u00f2ng c\u1ed5 v\u0169 b\u1ea1n trai l\u00e0 Mbappe.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean trong ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y v\u00e0i ng\u00e0y, Alicia \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u201cT\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 tin \u0111\u1ed3n. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 c\u00f3 m\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 n\u00e0o v\u1edbi Mbappe\u201d. Th\u1ef1c h\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o th\u00ec ch\u1eb3ng ai r\u00f5. C\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn l\u00e0 Mbappe \u0111ang t\u1eadp trung t\u1ed1i \u0111a cho s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7. Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o 19 tu\u1ed5i ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed1 m\u1eb9 qu\u1ea3n r\u1ea5t ch\u1eb7t trong vi\u1ec7c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng th\u1eddi gian ngo\u00e0i ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng.</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5333","checkdouble":"194185"},{"date":"16:12 10/08","title":"Th\u00eam 1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 HAGL \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed5 sung l\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/1/12/them-1-cau-thu-hagl-duoc-bo-sung-len-tuyen-olympic-viet-nam.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u00e0nh Chung b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd g\u1eb7p ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng s\u00e1t ng\u00e0y Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Tr\u1ea7n Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ea7y Park g\u1ecdi thay th\u1ebf.</h2><h2>Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ecdi b\u1ed5 sung l\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ecdi b\u1ed5 sung l\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ecdi b\u1ed5 sung l\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/11/10/Minh-Vuong-duoc-goi-bo-sung-len-tuyen-Olympic-Viet-Nam-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Park Hang Seo\u00a0g\u1ecdi b\u1ed5 sung l\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a,<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-viet-nam/olympic-viet-nam-co-them-ca-chan-thuong-truoc-khi-len-duong-du-asiad-168-194157.html\" target=\"_blank\"> h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u00e0nh Chung \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng</span> trong bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp di\u1ec5n ra chi\u1ec1u qua 9/8. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y bu\u1ed9c HLV Park Hang Seo ph\u1ea3i l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 thay th\u1ebf, v\u00e0 g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u2018v\u00e9 v\u1edbt\u2019 c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng Park l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Tr\u1ea7n Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a HAGL.</div>\r\n<p>Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u0169ng l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 t\u00ean trong danh s\u00e1ch 30 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Park Hang Seo g\u1ecdi v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u1edf gi\u1ea3i U23 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf 2018 m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y. Tuy nhi\u00ean, khi \u00f4ng Park ch\u1ed1t danh s\u00e1ch xu\u1ed1ng c\u00f2n 20 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7, Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i do kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng nh\u1eadn \u2018v\u00e9 v\u1edbt\u2019 l\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n, qu\u00e2n s\u1ed1 HAGL \u0111\u00e3 g\u1ed3m 5 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 l\u00e0 Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng, V\u0103n To\u00e0n, V\u0103n Thanh v\u00e0 L\u01b0\u01a1ng Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng, trong khi s\u1ed1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 thu\u1ed9c bi\u00ean ch\u1ebf CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam r\u00fat xu\u1ed1ng c\u00f2n 7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch, h\u00f4m nay (10/8) U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd c\u00f3 th\u00eam 1 bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp t\u1ea1i B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng. Sau \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng sang Indonesia v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 11/8. Theo l\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t g\u1eb7p Pakistan, Nepal v\u00e0 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n v\u00e0o c\u00e1c ng\u00e0y 14, 16 v\u00e0 19/8.\u00a0V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c c\u1ea3 Nepal v\u00e0 Pakistan \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 m\u1ea1nh, O. Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n s\u1ebd d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/bao-indonesia-danh-gia-cao-dt-olympic-viet-nam-tai-asiad-168-194114.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/9/bao-indonesia-danh-gia-cao-dt-olympic-viet-nam-tai-asiad.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/bao-indonesia-danh-gia-cao-dt-olympic-viet-nam-tai-asiad-168-194114.html\">B\u00e1o Indonesia \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD</span><br>\r\nT\u1edd b\u00e1o Bola c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 ASIAD 2018 m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)\u00a0<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\nline-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5332","checkdouble":"194181"},{"date":"16:09 10/08","title":"S\u1ebfp HAGL n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng nh\u1eadn \u2018v\u00e9 v\u1edbt\u2019 c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y Park?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2017/1/12/sep-hagl-noi-gi-khi-minh-vuong-nhan-ve-vot-cua-thay-park.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u01b0\u1edbc vi\u1ec7c ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Tr\u1ea7n Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Park Hang Seo tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp l\u00ean \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam, tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n HAGL \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c n\u00e0y.</h2><h2>S\u1ebfp HAGL n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng nh\u1eadn \u2018v\u00e9 v\u1edbt\u2019 c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y Park?</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong s\u1ed1 10 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i khi HLV Park Hang Seo ch\u1ed1t danh s\u00e1ch ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1ef1 ASIAD. Tuy nhi\u00ean v\u1eadn may \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi anh khi h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Th\u00e0nh Chung g\u1eb7p ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u00e0y, Th\u00e0nh Chung \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i l\u1ed7i h\u1eb9n v\u1edbi ASIAD 2018. V\u00e0 ngay trong s\u00e1ng nay, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh g\u1ecdi l\u1ea1i ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u1ebf ch\u1ed7 trong danh s\u00e1ch 20 tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 d\u1ef1 ASIAD.<br />\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"S\u1ebfp HAGL n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng nh\u1eadn \u2018v\u00e9 v\u1edbt\u2019 c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y Park h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"S\u1ebfp HAGL n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng nh\u1eadn \u2018v\u00e9 v\u1edbt\u2019 c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y Park h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/10/27/Sep-HAGL-noi-gi-khi-Minh-Vuong-nhan-\u2018ve-vot\u2019-cua-thay-Park-hinh-anh.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ecdi b\u1ed5 sung l\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam. \u1ea2nh: Nguy\u1ec5n \u0110\u0103ng.</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u00f3i v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec7n n\u00e0y, tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n HAGL Nguy\u1ec5n T\u1ea5n Anh \u0111\u00e3 chia s\u1ebb tr\u00ean b\u00e1o D\u00e2n Vi\u1ec7t: \u201cS\u00e1ng nay, anh L\u00ea Ho\u00e0i Anh \u2013 T\u1ed5ng th\u01b0 k\u00fd VFF \u0111\u00e3 g\u1ecdi \u0111i\u1ec7n th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o v\u1edbi CLB v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c HLV Park Hang-seo g\u1ecdi b\u1ed5 sung Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng. Hi\u1ec7n Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111ang di chuy\u1ec3n t\u1eeb qu\u00ea nh\u00e0 Th\u00e1i B\u00ecnh ra H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 bay \u0111i B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1eadp trung c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i ngay trong chi\u1ec1u nay\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00d4ng T\u1ea5n Anh c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ecdi b\u1ed5 sung s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u00f3 d\u1ecbp th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. \u201cTrong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho v\u00f2ng chung k\u1ebft U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m nay, HLV Park Hang-seo \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ea5m Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng may c\u1eadu ta l\u1ea1i d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng trong m\u1ed9t bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 sang Trung Qu\u1ed1c c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hy v\u1ecdng t\u1ea1i ASIAD s\u1eafp t\u1edbi, V\u01b0\u01a1ng s\u1ebd c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p trong l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i chung c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam\u201d, v\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n HAGL cho bi\u1ebft th\u00eam.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt \u1edf V-League m\u00f9a n\u00e0y. V\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u00fat ph\u1ea1t t\u1ed1t, l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i n\u0103ng n\u1ed5 v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u00e1o b\u1ea1o, \u0111\u1ea7y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd, Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd gi\u00fap HLV Park Hang Seo c\u00f3 th\u00eam s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng trong nh\u1eefng th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1i ASIAD.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: \"Open Sans\", sans-serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5331","checkdouble":"194186"},{"date":"13:24 10/08","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Marseille vs Toulouse 01h45 ng\u00e0y 11/8 (Ligue 1 2018/19)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ph\u00e1p","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/10/nhan-dinh-marseille-vs-toulouse-01h45-ngay-118-ligue-1-201819.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Marseille vs Toulouse l\u00fac 01h45 ng\u00e0y 11/8 (V\u00f2ng 1 gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG Ph\u00e1p Ligue 1 2018/19): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Marseille vs Toulouse 01h45 ng\u00e0y 118 Ligue 1 201819 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Marseille vs Toulouse 01h45 ng\u00e0y 118 Ligue 1 201819 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/10/marseille-toulouse.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Marseille vs Toulouse</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> </span></span></span></span></span>Marseille vs Toulouse: 3-1<br>\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n<div>Kh\u00e1c v\u1edbi m\u1ecdi n\u0103m, m\u00f9a n\u00e0y Marseille ch\u1ecdn c\u00e1c \u201cqu\u00e2n xanh\u201d r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 ch\u01a1i \u0111\u1ec3 HLV Garcia th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh. V\u1edbi t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t t\u1eeb m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u1edf l\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Velodrome, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 ch\u01a1i \u0111a d\u1ea1ng, phong ph\u00fa h\u01a1n, n\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 li\u00ean t\u1ee5c th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n nh\u1eefng thay \u0111\u1ed5i c\u1ea3 v\u1ec1 con ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u1eabn chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt tr\u01b0\u1edbc 7 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 trong su\u1ed1t 1 th\u00e1ng qua. H\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c Nantes 2-1 l\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng duy nh\u1ea5t trong chu\u1ed7i tr\u1eadn n\u00f3i tr\u00ean, song HLV Garcia thu v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng t\u00edn hi\u1ec7u r\u1ea5t l\u1ea1c quan. D\u00f9 3 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t Steve Mandanda, Adil Rami v\u00e0 Florian Thauvin v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t \u1edf giai \u0111o\u1ea1n ch\u1ea1y \u0111\u00e0 (ngh\u1ec9 H\u00e8 sau khi v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018 c\u00f9ng \u0110T Ph\u00e1p), nh\u01b0ng Marseille v\u1eabn thi \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng n\u00e9t tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 kh\u00f3 ch\u01a1i nh\u01b0 St.Etienne, Villarreal, Betis, Sporting hay Bournemouth. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nMarseille c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1eafng, nh\u01b0ng lu\u00f4n ghi b\u00e0n v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o s\u1ee9c \u00e9p r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t l\u00ean \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. HLV Garcia nh\u1ea5n m\u1ea1nh r\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 giao h\u1eefu kh\u00f4ng \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ebfn t\u00e2m l\u00fd thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Marseille. \u201cC\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi. Ngay c\u1ea3 khi Rami, Mandanda v\u00e0 Thauvin v\u1eeba h\u1ebft k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 H\u00e8 v\u00e0 ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u0111\u00eam nay, Marseille c\u0169ng v\u1eabn t\u1ef1 tin khu\u1ea5t ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Toulouse\u201d, HLV Garcia cho bi\u1ebft tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf t\u00e2m l\u00fd v\u00e0 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, Marseille \u0111ang s\u1edf h\u1eefu th\u00e0nh t\u00edch r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0.\u00a0 19 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i Velodrome \u1edf gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG Ph\u00e1p, h\u1ecd th\u1eafng 12, h\u00f2a 5 v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 thua 2 (tr\u01b0\u1edbc Lyon v\u00e0 Rennes). Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed, ngay c\u1ea3 \u1edf 15 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi Toulouse, Marseille \u0111\u1ec1u b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i v\u1edbi 8 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 7 tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a. V\u00e0 l\u1ea7n g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t Toulouse \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Marseille t\u1ea1i Velodrome c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 h\u01a1n 6 n\u0103m khi h\u1ecd th\u1eafng t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u 1-0 \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 m\u00f9a 2011/12 v\u00e0o th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ea5t c\u1ea3ng \u0111ang kh\u1ee7ng ho\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, Toulouse v\u1eeba m\u1ea5t 2 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t \u1edf h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7. Trung v\u1ec7 Issa Diop (West Ham) v\u00e0 th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Alban Lafont (Fiorentina) ra \u0111i l\u00e0 t\u1ed5n th\u1ea5t c\u1ef1c l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi Toulouse \u1edf m\u00f9a n\u00e0y. D\u00f9 m\u1ea5t 2 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a HLV Alain Casanova v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung n\u00e0o bu\u1ed9c \u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng \u201cc\u00e2y nh\u00e0 l\u00e1 v\u01b0\u1eddn\u201d \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1eafp gh\u00e9p \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh h\u00e0nh qu\u00e2n t\u1edbi Marseille \u0111\u00eam nay. M\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Toulouse ph\u1ea3i n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ebfn v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng m\u1edbi tr\u1ee5 l\u1ea1i Ligue 1. H\u00e8 n\u00e0y, h\u1ecd m\u1ea5t \u0111i nh\u1eefng m\u1eaft x\u00edch then ch\u1ed1t v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb k\u1ef9 c\u00e0ng cho m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi. So v\u1ec1 m\u1ecdi kh\u00eda c\u1ea1nh, Toulouse \u0111ang k\u00e9m h\u01a1n Marseille r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u. Xem ra, l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y h\u1ecd s\u1ebd b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 nh\u1ea5n ch\u00ecm \u1edf \u201cch\u1ea3o l\u1eeda\u201d Velodrome.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTH\u00d4NG TIN<br>\r\nL\u01b0\u1edbi rung cu\u1ed1i hi\u1ec7p 1<br>\r\n10/11 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Marseille v\u00e0 7/10 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y c\u1ee7a Toulouse c\u00f3 \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng t\u1eeb ph\u00fat 16-45. Ngo\u00e0i ra, 15/16 tr\u1eadn s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Marseille c\u0169ng ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u 1 l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1edbi rung 30 ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i hi\u1ec7p 1. Xem ra tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 ngo\u1ea1i l\u1ec7.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1eb6C BI\u1ec6T<br>\r\nTheo k\u00e8o ch\u00e2u \u00c1, Marseille th\u1eafng 6, h\u00f2a 3, thua 11 \u1edf 20 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t; Toulouse th\u1eafng 4, h\u00f2a 4, thua 12 \u1edf 20 tr\u1eadn v\u1eeba qua.<br>\r\nTr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0, Marseille th\u1eafng 10, h\u00f2a 2, thua 8 \u1edf 20 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y theo k\u00e8o ch\u00e2u \u00c1.<br>\r\nTr\u00ean s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch, Toulouse th\u1eafng 3, h\u00f2a 3, thua 14 \u1edf 20 tr\u1eadn v\u1eeba qua theo k\u00e8o ch\u00e2u \u00c1.</div>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5330","checkdouble":"194174"},{"date":"14:34 10/08","title":"MU chi ti\u1ec1n kh\u1ee7ng mua sao PSG nh\u01b0ng b\u1ecb t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/16/soc-mu-chi-tien-khung-mua-mbappe-nhung-bi-tu-choi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Theo tin t\u1eeb t\u1edd Mirror, Man United \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Mbappe h\u00e8 v\u1eeba qua nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Man United \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i khi ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 3 t\u00e2n binh l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Fred, sao tr\u1ebb Diogo Dalot v\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb Lee Grant. Mourinho mong mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 m\u1edbi nh\u01b0ng \u01b0\u1edbc mu\u1ed1n n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nR\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch ban l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o MU v\u00e0 cho r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ng\u1ea7n ng\u1ea1i chi ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ee7ng c\u1ed1 s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh. Nh\u01b0ng m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, t\u1edd Mirror kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00e0nh Ed Woodward \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng \u0111\u01b0a sao tr\u1ebb ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng Mbappe v\u1ec1 s\u00e2n Old Trafford.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"MU chi ti\u1ec1n kh\u1ee7ng mua ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Mbappe nh\u01b0ng b\u1ecb t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"MU chi ti\u1ec1n kh\u1ee7ng mua ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Mbappe nh\u01b0ng b\u1ecb t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/16/soc-mu-chi-tien-khung-mua-mbappe-nhung-bi-tu-choi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>MU mua Mbappe kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tu\u1ed5i teen n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi PSG t\u1eeb Monaco h\u00e8 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n. V\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i t\u1edbi m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y, anh m\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 Paris mua \u0111\u1ee9t v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 160 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMbappe \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn sau k\u1ef3 World Cup \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p. Real Madrid c\u0169ng nh\u1eafm Mbappe thay th\u1ebf si\u00eau sao Cristiano Ronaldo t\u1ea1i Bernabeu.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMan United c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eedi m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb cho PSG h\u00e8 v\u1eeba qua nh\u01b0ng b\u1ecb t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i nhanh ch\u00f3ng. V\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn Woodward ph\u1ea3i suy ngh\u0129 l\u1ea1i v\u1ec1 c\u00e1ch x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Man United.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Mourinho, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf th\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u1eafm \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng v\u00e0 c\u00f3 kinh nghi\u1ec7m thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ec9nh cao nh\u01b0 Zlatan Ibrahimovic hay Alexis Sanchez. Nh\u01b0ng b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u00e0 PSG d\u00e0nh cho Mbappe cho th\u1ea5y nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ea1i gia kh\u00e1c \u1edf ch\u00e2u \u00c2u \u0111ang s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng nu\u00f4i d\u01b0\u1ee1ng nh\u1eefng t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ea1i k\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ecbch Man City c\u0169ng \u0111ang ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t l\u1ee9a tr\u1ebb \u0111\u1ea7y ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng. V\u00e0 Woodward quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eb1ng Man United c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i \u01b0u ti\u00ean s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng &ldquo;g\u00e0 nh\u00e0&rdquo; nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n. \u0110\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn Man United t\u1ecf ra kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y m\u1eb7n m\u00e0 v\u1edbi th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Man United:<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/harry-maguire-noi-gi-khi-khong-the-den-mu-172-194172.html\">Harry Maguire n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn MU</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/tiet-lo-ly-do-mu-khong-mua-alderweireld-va-ivan-perisic-172-194171.html\">Ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 l\u00fd do MU kh\u00f4ng mua Alderweireld v\u00e0 Ivan Perisic</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n</strong><br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5329","checkdouble":"194175"},{"date":"16:23 10/08","title":"B\u1ecb nh\u0103m nhe c\u01b0\u1edbp Modric, Real ph\u1ea3n \u0111\u00f2n Inter","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/1/17/real-madrid-dam-phan-mua-mauro-icardi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Real Madrid \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n mua Mauro Icardi. \u0110\u00e2y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i ph\u1ea3n \u0111\u00f2n c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia T\u00e2y Ban Nha khi tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t Luka Modric b\u1ecb Inter Milan ve v\u00e3n.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Inter mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Modric</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nCh\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Luka Modric t\u1ea1i Real Madrid v\u00e0 \u0110T Croatia, Inter Milan kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ng\u1ed3i y\u00ean. H\u1ecd li\u00ean t\u1ee5c ch\u00e8o k\u00e9o ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y b\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb kh\u00f3 ch\u1ed1i t\u1eeb. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, Inter s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng tr\u1ea3 cho Modric m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u00ean t\u1edbi 10 tri\u1ec7u Euro, g\u1ea7n g\u1ea5p \u0111\u00f4i nh\u1eefng g\u00ec anh \u0111ang l\u0129nh t\u1ea1i Real (6,5 tri\u1ec7u Euro) trong h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 4 n\u0103m. Ch\u01b0a h\u1ebft, Nerazzurri c\u00f2n h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n s\u1ebd gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Croatia v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ea1i gia Trung Qu\u1ed1c khi mu\u1ed1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Real Madrid \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n mua Mauro Icardi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Real Madrid \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n mua Mauro Icardi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/7/Real-Madrid-dam-phan-mua-Mauro-Icardi-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Inter mu\u1ed1n Modric c\u1ee7a Real</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Real ph\u1ea3n \u0111\u00f2n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u1ed9t m\u1eb7t, Real t\u00ecm m\u1ecdi c\u00e1ch gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n Modric tr\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1ef1 s\u0103n \u0111\u00f3n c\u1ee7a Inter Milan. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 Mateo Kovacic t\u1edbi Chelsea d\u01b0\u1edbi d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c thi\u1ebfu h\u1ee5t nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1eb7t kh\u00e1c, Real Madrid \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n mua Mauro Icardi. Sau s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a Cristiano Ronaldo, Los Blancos \u0111ang c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y thi\u1ebfu m\u1ed9t c\u00e2y s\u0103n b\u00e0n \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 khi Karim Benzema ng\u00e0y m\u1ed9t k\u00e9m duy\u00ean. M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00e0 h\u1ecd nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi h\u00e8 n\u00e0y ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 Icardi, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ghi t\u1edbi 100 b\u00e0n sau 159 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n cho Inter k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi gia nh\u1eadp m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m 2014.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"tien dao Icardi\" title=\"tien dao Icardi\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/1/17/real-madrid-dam-phan-mua-mauro-icardi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Real Madrid \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n mua Mauro Icardi</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc 2017/18, Icardi ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n phong \u0111\u1ed9 l\u00e0m b\u00e0n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Anh ghi t\u1edbi 29 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng cho Inter ch\u1ec9 sau 34 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n t\u1ea1i Serie A, \u0111\u1ed3ng Vua ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi c\u00f9ng Ciro Immobile. \u0110i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i v\u1edbi Inter l\u00e0 100 tri\u1ec7u Euro.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, Real \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1eaft t\u1edbi Icardi trong m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m th\u00edch h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia hi\u1ec7n th\u1ef1c h\u00f3a \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 khi t\u00e2n HLV Julen Lopetegui c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina.<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real tr\u00ean trang bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/thibaut-courtois-chinh-thuc-ra-mat-real-madrid-180-194131.html\">Thibaut Courtois CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C ra m\u1eaft Real Madrid</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/quan-diem-chelsea-muon-duoc-kovacic-tu-real-172-194124.html\">Quan \u0111i\u1ec3m: \u201cGi\u00e1o s\u01b0\u201d Kovacic l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t m\u00f3n h\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Chelsea</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-sau-thuong-vu-courtois-toi-real-madrid-172-194113.html\">3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Courtois t\u1edbi Real Madrid</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-madrid-muon-giu-chan-luka-modric-180-194111.html\">Real n\u00edu k\u00e9o Modric \u1edf l\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1ef1 ch\u00e8o k\u00e9o c\u1ee7a Inter</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/chuyen-nhuong-real-madrid-hot-nhat-ngay-0908-180-194097.html\">Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid hot nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 09/08</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5328","checkdouble":"194183"},{"date":"16:50 10/08","title":"B\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 ai c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf Luka Modric","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/16/robert-jarni-phat-bieu-ve-real-madrid-va-luka-modric.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Robert Jarni ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Real Madrid v\u00e0 Luka Modric. C\u1ef1u tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Croatia c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o g\u00e3 kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3 T\u00e2y Ban Nha s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n trong vi\u1ec7c gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n ng\u00f4i sao s\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Modric b\u1ecb Inter ch\u00e8o k\u00e9o</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, Luka Modric \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1. Anh l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u00e0u c\u1ee7a \u0110T Croatia v\u00e0 c\u00f9ng h\u1ecd \u0111i t\u1edbi chung k\u1ebft c\u1ee7a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga. D\u00f9 \u0111\u1ec3 thua Ph\u00e1p 2-4 song c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n Modric v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00f4n vinh v\u1edbi danh hi\u1ec7u Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng v\u00e0ng World Cup 2018 (t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t).<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNgay sau \u0111\u00f3, Inter Milan l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Modric. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Italia nh\u00e2n d\u1ecbp tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Champions League sau 6 n\u0103m r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n c\u1ee7ng c\u1ed1 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng b\u1eb1ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 3 n\u0103m li\u1ec1n v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Real. C\u0169ng xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n ngu\u1ed3n tin r\u1eb1ng ch\u00ednh Modric \u0111\u00e3 y\u00eau c\u1ea7u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra \u0111i, gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p c\u1ee7a c\u1ef1u \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i Cristiano Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 112 tri\u1ec7u Euro.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Robert Jarni ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Real Madrid v\u00e0 Luka Modric h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Robert Jarni ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Real Madrid v\u00e0 Luka Modric h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/16/robert-jarni-phat-bieu-ve-real-madrid-va-luka-modric.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Modric t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Real nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi khuy\u00ean</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nRobert Jarni ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Real Madrid v\u00e0 Luka Modric. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u1eebng 81 l\u1ea7n kho\u00e1c \u00e1o \u0110T Croatia tin r\u1eb1ng h\u1eadu b\u1ed1i Modric s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p ra \u0111i trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. \u0110\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n l\u00e0 b\u1edfi Real kh\u00f4ng t\u00ecm ra \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf anh trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai g\u1ea7n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang ta bi\u1ebft th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u00e0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o\u201d, anh n\u00f3i v\u1edbi Cadena SER. \u201cT\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng tin v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n r\u1eb1ng Luka Modric s\u1ebd ra \u0111i. T\u00f4i bi\u1ebft c\u1eadu \u1ea5y d\u00e0nh nhi\u1ec1u t\u00ecnh c\u1ea3m cho Real Madrid v\u00e0 CLB c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o thay th\u1ebf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho c\u1eadu \u1ea5y.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Luka Modric\" title=\"Luka Modric\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/7/Real-Madrid-dam-phan-mua-Mauro-Icardi-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Robert Jarni ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Real Madrid v\u00e0 Luka Modric</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y \u00edt ng\u00e0y, Real \u0111\u00e3 cho ph\u00e9p Mateo Kovacic gia nh\u1eadp Chelsea d\u01b0\u1edbi d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n 1 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i. V\u1edbi Jarni, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia s\u1ebd thu \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ee3i \u00edch t\u1eeb vi\u1ec7c tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m t\u1ea1i CLB Premier League.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cMateo Kovacic l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng song ch\u00fang ta v\u1eabn ph\u1ea3i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i c\u1eadu \u1ea5y tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh h\u01a1n\u201d, c\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh 49 tu\u1ed5i n\u00f3i th\u00eam. \u201c\u0110\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f2n qu\u00e1 tr\u1ebb, thi\u1ebfu kinh nghi\u1ec7m song \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean ra s\u00e2n. V\u1edbi Modric \u1edf Real, Kovac c\u00e0ng kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i h\u01a1n.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real tr\u00ean trang bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/tiet-lo-max-allegri-da-tu-choi-real-madrid-mua-he-nay-184-194164.html\">Ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9: Max Allegri \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i Real Madrid m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/thibaut-courtois-chinh-thuc-ra-mat-real-madrid-180-194131.html\">Thibaut Courtois CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C ra m\u1eaft Real Madrid</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/quan-diem-chelsea-muon-duoc-kovacic-tu-real-172-194124.html\">Quan \u0111i\u1ec3m: \u201cGi\u00e1o s\u01b0\u201d Kovacic l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t m\u00f3n h\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Chelsea</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-chieu-mo-kovacic-bai-toan-kho-danh-cho-sarri-172-194118.html\">Chelsea chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Kovacic: HLV Sarri \u0111\u1ed1i di\u1ec7n b\u00e0i to\u00e1n kh\u00f3 gi\u1ea3i</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-sau-thuong-vu-courtois-toi-real-madrid-172-194113.html\">3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Courtois t\u1edbi Real Madrid</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5327","checkdouble":"194189"},{"date":"17:33 10/08","title":"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Barca hot nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 10/08","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/1/chuyen-nhuong-barca-hot-nhat-ngay-1008.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Barca 2018 \u0111ang ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng kh\u00e1 s\u00f4i n\u1ed5i, c\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec3m qua tin \u0111\u1ed3n li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou hot nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 10/08.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Barca t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n Thomas Vermaelen</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Barca 2018 hot nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 1008 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Barca 2018 hot nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 1008 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/31/Chuyen-nhuong-Barca-2018-hot-nhat-ngay-1008-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Barca kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Thomas Vermaelen</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nCrystal Palace \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ecfi m\u01b0\u1ee3n Thomas Vermaelen, song Barca kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Andre Gomes t\u1edbi Everton theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Andre Gomes r\u1eddi Barca t\u1edbi Everton theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 1 m\u00f9a, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 C\u1ea3ng \u0111\u00e3 chi ra 2.25 tri\u1ec7u euro v\u00e0 tr\u1ea3 to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 ti\u1ec1n l\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i \u0111ang nh\u1eadn \u1edf s\u00e2n Camp Nou.<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-bom-xit-barca-cap-ben-ngoai-hang-anh-172-194141.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/9/chinh-thuc-bom-xit-barca-cap-ben-ngoai-hang-anh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-bom-xit-barca-cap-ben-ngoai-hang-anh-172-194141.html\">CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C: Bom x\u1ecbt Barca c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh</span><br>\r\nAndre Gomes r\u1eddi Barca t\u1edbi Everton theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 1 m\u00f9a, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 C\u1ea3ng \u0111\u00e3 chi ra 2.25 tri\u1ec7u euro v\u00e0 tr\u1ea3 to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 ti\u1ec1n l\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Mina ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c t\u1edbi Everton v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 30 tri\u1ec7u euro</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Yerry Mina r\u1eddi Barca t\u1edbi Everton, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 24 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 5 n\u0103m v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Goodison Park. Barca \u0111\u00e3 thu v\u1ec1 30,2 tri\u1ec7u euro t\u1eeb th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>2 \u0111\u1ea1i gia Ligue 1 \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn v\u00ec sao Barca</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ivan Rakitic r\u1eddi Barca, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 mong mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 PSG v\u00e0 Monaco. Hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Ligue 1 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi \u0111\u1eadm mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Barca c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn v\u1ee5 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u1ee7a Liverpool</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Napoli mu\u1ed1n mua Simon Mignolet, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Italia ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 11 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 v\u1edbi Barca.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Barca kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Alba cho MU</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"hau ve Jordi Alba\" title=\"hau ve Jordi Alba\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/30/Tin-chuyen-nhuong-hom-nay-ngay-88,-tin-chuyen-nhuong-he-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Barca kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ea3 Jordi Alba cho MU</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1edd Daily Star \u0111\u01b0a tin Man United \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i Jordi Alba \u0111\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf cho Luke Shaw, song Barca \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh cho Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Sao kh\u1ee7ng Barca ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0a ra c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi cho Arsenal</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u01b0a tin ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Ousmane Dembele s\u1ebd t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i s\u1ef1 ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn t\u1eeb Arsenal v\u00e0 \u1edf l\u1ea1i Barcelona th\u00eam m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u1eefa.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>HLV Valverde mu\u1ed1n &ldquo;d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb h\u1ea1ng sang&rdquo; \u1edf l\u1ea1i Barca</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Valverde mu\u1ed1n Cillessen \u1edf l\u1ea1i Barca. Thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Blaugrana mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 c\u1ea1nh tranh \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c n\u1eb7ng d\u00e0nh cho th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n s\u1ed1 1 Marc-Andre ter Stegen.<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Jasper Cillessen\" title=\"Jasper Cillessen\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/7/HLV-Valverde-muon-Cillessen-o-lai-Barca-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Barca mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef Jasper Cillessen</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Barca v\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Paul Pogba</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo Mirror, chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Barca 2018 v\u1eabn quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Paul Pogba c\u1ee7a M.U. \u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng chi t\u1edbi 130 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua ng\u00f4i sao 25 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5326","checkdouble":"194195"},{"date":"15:38 10/08","title":"MU kh\u00f4ng mua s\u1eafm r\u1ea7m r\u1ed9, Smalling v\u1eabn th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/2/27/mu-khong-mua-sam-ram-ro-smalling-van-thach-thuc-nhung-doi-thu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chris Smalling ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 MU, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh d\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1eefng t\u00e2n binh ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf v\u1eabn \u0111\u1ee7 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">MU kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u t\u00e2n binh kh\u1ee7ng \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018, HLV Jose Mourinho \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 s\u1ebd c\u00f3 150 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 mua s\u1eafm c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7. \u00d4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 4 t\u00e2n binh ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, tuy nhi\u00ean <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/mourinho-bi-quan-ve-kha-nang-mua-them-nguoi-172-194120.html\" target=\"_blank\">BL\u0110 Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn c\u1ef1u HLV Chelsea h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng</span>.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chris Smalling ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 MU tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 201819 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chris Smalling ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 MU tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 201819 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/9/Chris-Smalling-phat-bieu-ve-MU-truoc-mua-giai-201819-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mourinho kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM.U \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018 kh\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng, h\u1ecd nhanh ch\u00f3ng \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 Fred v\u00e0 Dalot. B\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf ph\u1ea3i chi 71 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Tuy nhi\u00ean, trong th\u1eddi gian c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 th\u00eam duy nh\u1ea5t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Lee Grant.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nH\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi nh\u01b0 Toby Alderweireld, Yerry Mina, Jerome Boateng, Harry Magui, Willian, Ivan Perisic, Sergej Milinkovic-Savic... l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a Man \u0111\u1ecf, nh\u01b0ng BL\u0110 M.U kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ebfn Old Trafford.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u01b0 v\u1eady l\u00e0 sau r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m, M.U m\u1edbi c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1ea3m \u0111\u1ea1m. V\u1edbi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n chi ra kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 l\u1edbn, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111ang b\u1ecb t\u1ee5t l\u1ea1i so v\u1edbi Man City v\u00e0 Liverpool trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua t\u1edbi danh hi\u1ec7u Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh m\u00f9a t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Smalling kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh M.U m\u00f9a t\u1edbi v\u1eabn r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chris Smalling ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 MU, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh d\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1eefng t\u00e2n binh ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf v\u1eabn \u0111\u1ee7 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Smalling vs Tottenham\" title=\"Smalling vs Tottenham\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/23/Tin-chuyen-nhuong-hom-nay-ngay-18,-tin-chuyen-nhuong-he-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Smalling tin M.U v\u1eabn r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c\u0110\u00fang l\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng l\u1edbn, song v\u1ec1 c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n M.U v\u1eabn gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng. \u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 x\u00e1o tr\u1ed9n so v\u1edbi m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u, t\u00f4i tin \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cNhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng M.U b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p do kh\u00f4ng mua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn, nh\u01b0ng theo t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i v\u1eady. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng s\u1ebd l\u00e0 sai l\u1ea7m n\u1ebfu \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p M.U, t\u00f4i t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0o kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ea1nh tranh c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5325","checkdouble":"194177"},{"date":"15:47 10/08","title":"Emery \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch NHA cho Arsenal","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/28/hlv-emery-phat-bieu-ve-muc-tieu-cua-arsenal.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Unai Emery ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a Arsenal. \u00d4ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh mu\u1ed1n gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh, nh\u01b0ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 th\u1eadt phong c\u00e1ch.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>\u0110\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch NHA</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Arsenal ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ee9ng ngo\u00e0i t\u1ed1p 4 c\u1ee7a gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh. Qua \u0111\u00f3, h\u1ecd c\u00f3 m\u00f9a th\u1ee9 2 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng Champions League. Cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a, HLV Arsenen Wenger tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u00e1p l\u1ef1c t\u1eeb ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i l\u1eddi t\u1eeb ch\u1ee9c sau 22 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u sau, Unai Emery \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m l\u00e0m HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng Arsenal. M\u1ed9t k\u1ef7 nguy\u00ean m\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1edf ra v\u00e0 nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha kh\u00f4ng gi\u1ea5u tham v\u1ecdng chinh ph\u1ee5c ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh d\u00f9 nh\u1ea5n m\u1ea1nh Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 c\u1ea7n th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 v\u1edbi kh\u00ed ch\u1ea5t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Unai Emery ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a Arsenal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Unai Emery ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a Arsenal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/28/hlv-emery-phat-bieu-ve-muc-tieu-cua-arsenal.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>HLV Emery ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a Arsenal</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cM\u1ee5c \u0111\u00edch c\u1ee7a CLB l\u00e0 v\u00e0o gi\u1ea3i v\u1edbi m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch, ch\u01a1i v\u00ec c\u00e1c danh hi\u1ec7u\u201d, Emery ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a Arsenal. \u201cNh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi t\u00f4i, t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n t\u1eadn h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 t\u1eadn h\u01b0\u1edfng c\u00f9ng nhau c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, t\u1eebng kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc tr\u00ean s\u00e2n. Th\u00f4ng qua \u0111\u00f3, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd truy\u1ec1n t\u1ea3i cho C\u0110V c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh ni\u1ec1m \u0111am m\u00ea b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1.\u201d<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 phong c\u00e1ch ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea1o</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nEmery \u0111ang c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng \u00e1p \u0111\u1eb7t tri\u1ebft l\u00fd ri\u00eang c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh sau khi ti\u1ebfp qu\u1ea3n Arsenal t\u1eeb Wenger. \u00d4ng ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng m\u1ed9t l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i thi\u00ean v\u1ec1 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng. \u201cPhong c\u00e1ch ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u1ea7m b\u00f3ng, ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u\u201d, c\u1ef1u thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng PSG n\u00f3i v\u1edbi Sky Sports.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cSau \u0111\u00f3 n\u1ebfu c\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng gian, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd t\u00edch c\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfn v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc. V\u1ec1 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean l\u00e0 t\u00ednh t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c, thu h\u1ed3i b\u00f3ng m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch nhanh ch\u00f3ng. Nh\u01b0ng trong m\u1ed7i kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c. D\u0129 nhi\u00ean, n\u00f3i lu\u00f4n d\u1ec5 h\u01a1n l\u00e0m. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n th\u1eddi gian, nh\u01b0ng l\u00fac n\u00e0y t\u00f4i h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac v\u00ec c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang ng\u00e0y m\u1ed9t ho\u00e0n hi\u1ec7n.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Arsenal tr\u00ean trang bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/dau-la-ban-hop-dong-xuat-sac-nhat-mua-he-2018-172-194147.html\">\u0110\u00e2u l\u00e0 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2018?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-west-ham-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-sao-arsenal-172-194121.html\">CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C: West Ham chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng bom x\u1ecbt c\u1ee7a Arsenal</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-va-chelsea-buon-vui-lan-lon-vu-aaron-ramsey-172-194087.html\">Arsenal v\u00e0 Chelsea bu\u1ed3n vui l\u1eabn l\u1ed9n v\u1ee5 Aaron Ramsey</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-giu-chan-ramsey-vi-chuyen-mon-va-mot-loi-khang-dinh-172-194026.html\">Arsenal gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n Ramsey: V\u00ec chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5324","checkdouble":"194178"},{"date":"16:13 10/08","title":"Sao tr\u1ebb kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ee1 t\u00e2n binh Fred c\u1ee7a M.U","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/6/sao-tre-khang-dinh-se-giup-do-tan-binh-fred-cua-mu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i Premier League, sao tr\u1ebb Andreas Pereira mu\u1ed1n gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ee1 Fred s\u1edbm h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp t\u1ea1i m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng m\u1edbi.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nM.U v\u00e0 c\u1eb7p ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Brazil<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng ho\u1eb7c v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111ang g\u1eb7p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n trong vi\u1ec7c s\u1eafp x\u1ebfp \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh. G\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn, 2 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Brazil l\u00e0 Andreas Pereira v\u00e0 Fred s\u1ebd g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t \u1edf h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi. C\u00e1i t\u00ean c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 sao tr\u1ebb Scott McTominay.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u00f3i c\u00e1ch kh\u00e1c, t\u00e2n binh \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3 nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a M.U trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y &ndash; Fred s\u1ebd l\u00e0 ni\u1ec1m hy v\u1ecdng l\u1edbn trong tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Leicester. Trong m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00e3 qua, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea7n n\u00e0o ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng pha tho\u00e1t pressing r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t, c\u0169ng nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n s\u00e1ng n\u01b0\u1edbc.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i m\u1edbi ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c th\u00edch nghi nhanh ch\u00f3ng, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng Andreas Pereira s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ee1 t\u1eadn t\u00ecnh. Sao tr\u1ebb m\u1edbi tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 t\u1eeb Valencia cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;Fred \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb qu\u1ed1c gia c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi t\u00f4i, v\u00ec v\u1eady t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap anh \u1ea5y r\u1ea5t d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng. T\u00f4i s\u1ebd n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap Fred h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp v\u1edbi cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng m\u1edbi.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<div style=\"width: 100%;\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Andreas Pereira mu\u1ed1n gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ee1 h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp t\u1ed1t\" title=\"Andreas Pereira cua MU\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/27/sao-tre-andreas-pereira-muon-roi-mu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Andreas Pereira mu\u1ed1n gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ee1 h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp t\u1ed1t</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u00f4i \u0111ang c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn anh \u1ea5y tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i nh\u01b0 \u1edf nh\u00e0, t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n Fred c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n v\u00e0 h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng m\u1edbi. Anh \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ch\u00e0ng trai t\u1ed1t, \u0111ang gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch h\u1ecdc ti\u1ebfng Anh. Fred c\u0169ng \u0111ang c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp v\u1edbi Man United.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f9ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3, sao tr\u1ebb c\u0169ng t\u1ef1 tin h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi, sau khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Jose Mourinho gi\u1eef l\u1ea1i thay v\u00ec ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u1eedi \u0111i cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n: &ldquo;T\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i r\u1eb1ng, t\u00f4i \u0111ang h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i. T\u00f4i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u, b\u1edfi v\u1eady t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap CLB. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eafp x\u1ebfp \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed s\u1ed1 6 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u l\u1ea1 l\u1eabm, nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i v\u1eabn \u0111ang h\u1ecdc h\u1ecfi t\u1eebng ng\u00e0y.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi c\u1eb7p ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Selecao n\u01a1i tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa, c\u0169ng nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin Andreas Pereira mu\u1ed1n gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ee1 Fred, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn tuy\u1ebfn ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a M.U h\u00f4m nay s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/muon-tan-binh-alexis-sanchez-ngam-che-mu-da-khong-dep-172-194148.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/6/muon-tan-binh-alexis-sanchez-ngam-che-mu-da-khong-dep.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/muon-tan-binh-alexis-sanchez-ngam-che-mu-da-khong-dep-172-194148.html\">M\u01b0\u1ee3n t\u00e2n binh, Alexis Sanchez ng\u1ea7m ch\u00ea MU \u0111\u00e1 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1eb9p</span><br>\r\nNg\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Chile t\u1ea5m t\u1eafc khen ng\u1ee3i ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 52 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng Fred s\u1ebd mang \u0111\u1ebfn b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u1eb9p v\u1ed1n \u0111ang tr\u1ed1ng v\u1eafng \u1edf Old Trafford.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mourinho-len-tieng-ca-ngoi-tai-nang-cua-tan-binh-bom-tan-172-191993.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/21/mourinho-len-tieng-ca-ngoi-tai-nang-cua-tan-binh-bom-tan.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mourinho-len-tieng-ca-ngoi-tai-nang-cua-tan-binh-bom-tan-172-191993.html\">Mourinho l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng ca ng\u1ee3i t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a t\u00e2n binh bom t\u1ea5n</span><br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Man United &ndash; Jose Mourinho ca ng\u1ee3i Fred c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 qu\u00e2n b\u00e0i ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u00ec t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5323","checkdouble":"194180"}]}